Class GeocodeExchange

java.lang.Object

      net.rim.device.api.lbs.maps.server.exchange.TleServerExchange
          net.rim.device.api.lbs.maps.server.exchange.GeocodeExchange

public final class GeocodeExchange
extends TleServerExchange

Handles both the creation of the geocoding request and the parsing of the response to a geocoding query.

When a geocoding request is made through the Geocoder class, the response is an instance of this class. The results (success or failure) will be in the instance. You can then query the instance for the results.

Since:
BlackBerry API 7.0.0
